<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 80vw;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden; /* Ensures the container does not exceed viewport width */
      }

      .flex-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column; /* On smaller screens, switch to column layout */
        gap: 20px;
      }

      header {
        background-color: rgb(255, 165, 0);
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }

      main {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        color: white;
        margin: 0; /* Remove default margin */
      }

      p {
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0; /* Remove default margin */
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: rgb(255, 165, 0);
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #45a049;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        background-color: rgb(10, 23, 76);
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      }

      /* Media query for smaller screens */
      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          max-width: 90vw; /* Adjust container width for smaller screens */
        }

        .flex-row {
          gap: 10px; /* Reduce gap between elements */
        }

        main {
          padding: 15px; /* Adjust main padding */
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 1.5rem; /* Decrease heading font size */
        }

        p {
          font-size: 0.9rem; /* Decrease paragraph font size */
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <header>
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            src="https://all4onecareservices.co.uk/assets/img/images/horizonatal.png"
            srcSet="https://all4onecareservices.co.uk/assets/img/images/horizonatal.png"
            style="width: 200px; height: 100px; object-fit: contain"
            class="img"
            alt="Logo"
          />
        </header>

        <main>
          <p style="padding: 30px">
            Dear <%= emailOrName %>,<br /><br />

            We hope this email finds you well.<br /><br />

            We needed to take a moment to personally thank you for subscribing to
            our newsletter. Your decision to join our community means a lot to
            us, and we're thrilled to have you on board.<br /><br />

            Our newsletter is designed to keep you updated with the latest news,
            promotions, and exclusive content from All4One. We hope you find it
            valuable and informative.<br /><br />

            If you ever have any questions, feedback, or suggestions, please
            don't hesitate to reach out. We're here to assist you and ensure
            your experience with us is exceptional.<br /><br />

            Once again, thank you for subscribing to our newsletter. We look
            forward to staying connected with you!<br /><br />

            Best regards,<br />

            All4One Care Services<br />
            Tel: +44 (0) 1708987738
          </p>
        </main>
      </div>
      <footer>Â© 2021-2024 All4One. All rights reserved.</footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
